474
00:29:51,360 --> 00:29:52,446
Tidakkah anda masih mempunyai kerja untuk diselesaikan?

475
00:29:52,470 --> 00:29:53,576
- Pergi.
- Ayuh.

476
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:54,600
- Pergi.
- Jom pergi.

477
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:04,030
