494
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,686
Dan ia kelihatan berkhasiat.

495
00:31:08,710 --> 00:31:10,530
Saya berasa sangat bertenaga sekarang.

496
00:31:13,510 --> 00:31:15,180
Kakak Muda, Cikgu, datang dan cuba ini!

497
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:16,710
